name: Lowland Kodan Expertise
description:
When purchased, gain a stack of a Lowland Kodan Expertise and increase its duration by 4 hours, up to a maximum of 24 hours. If purchased at max stacks, only the 4-hour duration will be added. Each stack gives additive bonuses while in Janthir.

1: +10% Experience
2: +10% Karma
3: +10% Gold
4: Gain additional unique map material from kodan caches
5: Gain fury when directly striking an enemy with the warclaw's Battle Maul
6: Gain more collectable coins from kodan caches
7: +5% Damage vs. titanspawn

description:
Use this to sign your account up for weekly Janthir Wilds Launch Supply Drops. Receive the first drop immediately and three more between now and September 9.

First Drop:
A Janthir Wilds Contract Board, a Wild Roar Mount Select License, and 2 Heroic Boosters.
Second Drop:
A Black Lion Outfit Voucher, a Wisteria Spear Skin, and 3 Smooth Berry Dye Kits.
Third Drop:
A Void Corrupted Weapon Choice, a Black Lion Backpack and Glider Voucher, and a Communal Boost Bonfire.
Fourth Drop:
5 Black Lion Chest Keys, a Black Lion Weapons Voucher, and a Golden Black Lion Chest Key.
